<p id="eip-idm26181456"><strong>23. A</strong> –1.</p>
<p id="eip-idm101246112"><strong>24. C</strong> matched pairs, dependent groups.</p>
<p id="eip-idm94339280"><strong>25. D</strong> Reject <em data-effect="italics">H<sub>0</sub></em>. There is sufficient evidence to conclude that there is a difference in the mean scores.</p>
<p id="eip-idm117750656"><strong>26. C</strong> there is sufficient evidence to conclude that the proportion for males is higher than the proportion for females.</p>
<p id="eip-idm33461680"><strong>27. B</strong> no</p>
<p id="eip-idm217428672"><strong>28. B</strong> <em data-effect="italics">p</em>-value is close to 1.</p>
<p id="eip-idm300932784"><strong>29. B</strong> No</p>
<p id="eip-idm147930336"><strong>30. C</strong> <span class="os-math-in-para"><math display="inline"><semantics><mrow>
