<p id="eip-idm76360448"><strong>31. D</strong> We should not be estimating here.</p>
<p id="eip-idm80692320"><strong>32. A</strong></p>
<p id="eip-idm225978224"><strong>33. A</strong> The <em data-effect="italics">p</em>-value is &gt; 0.10. There is insufficient information to conclude that the distribution is not uniform.</p>
<p id="eip-idm133463360"><strong>34. C</strong> The test is to determine if the different groups have the same means.</p></section></section>  
